## Functionality

The script provides the following functions:

- Check the status of cloud providers (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud)
- Check the version of Kubernetes
- Check the status of the Kubernetes cluster
- Check the status of pods
- Check the status of nodes
- Check the status of deployments
- Check the status of ingresses
- Check the status of network policies
- Check security events
- Notify the security team about security incidents
- Investigate security incidents
- Remediate security incidents
- Generate a security report
- Run a vulnerability scan
- Enforce security policies
- Backup configuration
- Run compliance checks

Feel free to extend or modify the script to suit your specific cloud security engineering needs.
